Subject: Secunia Research: NJStar Word Processor Font Name Buffer Overflow


====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 20/02/2006

        - NJStar Word Processor Font Name Buffer Overflow -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
Severity.............................................................2
Description of Vulnerability.........................................3
Solution.............................................................4
Time Table...........................................................5
Credits..............................................................6
